00:23:02.881 --> 00:23:04.248
and that
was how many years ago?

00:23:04.248 --> 00:23:06.251
Shivani: That was back in 2006.

00:23:06.251 --> 00:23:08.420
We had about 11 lions
we were monitoring

00:23:08.420 --> 00:23:10.755
and now we're up
